[resource]
script = ExtResource("1_7glei")
release_version = "v1.2.1"
notes = "[TITLE]Items
Glowering Dagger's parry time will now increase with Evasiveness
  A more substantial change to the Dagger is currently being workshopped
Red Tape now takes 15% of your Laff away on use
Removed Red Tape's buffer of leaving you at 1 Laff before making you go sad
Sandwich will now only heal 30% of your laff
Slightly decreased the rarity of Unstoppable Gobstopper
[TITLE]Characters
Evasiveness-focused items will no longer reroll for Lil Oldman
[TITLE]Bosses
Tweaked how invincibility frames affect the Head of Security boss fight
  While invincible, you can:
    Step on skull spaces without taking damage
    Pass through Virtual Skelecogs during the Matching round
    Properly interact with the puzzle, whereas before you would not have been able to
  This change is fully exclusive to the Head of Security boss fight, invincibility frames cannot be used to bypass standard puzzles in any way
[TITLE]Facilities
The Cog Golf Course has received a small visual overhaul, and some new connector rooms
[TITLE]Tweaks
The run seed is now visible when going sad
Made the sand mole room in the Cog Golf Course slightly easier
Items weighted by Luck will now be affected by Luck buffs and debuffs in battle
Made shoes and boots slightly smaller in world
[TITLE]Bugfixes
Fixed an issue where rerolling a Pocket Prank quickly after swapping it out for Paint Bucket would cause a crash
Added some extra checks to prevent Lil Oldman from randomly exploding
The Life Insurance status effect will no longer last indefinitely after use
Fixed Motorcycle Boots activating when Big Foghorn was used
Fixed missing defeat message from sand moles in the Cog Golf Course
Fixed the sand mole room not opening the gate upon losing
Fixed an issue that allowed you to fire The Directors
Fixed a rare softlock in the Head of Security boss fight
Fixed a few collision bugs in the Molten Mint
Fixed a few floating chests in the Molten Mint
Fixed an issue where pranks like Toy Hammer & Big Foghorn couldn't interact with battles containing Proxy Cogs in the Molten Mint
Fixed jumps not tracking properly for an item achievement
Fixed Mystery Toon's unlock being impossible
  For context, the method of unlocking Mystery Toon is still to defeat The Directors as Moe Zart
Fixed Audio not playing on MacOS
Fixed an inconsistency with the alt-floor rate for White-Out and the standard alt-floor rate
Fixed an issue where after defeating The Liquidator, you were unable to backtrack through the facility, as the death floor was still active
Fixed an issue where the Molten Mint music would continue on after the Facility ended if you wound up in The Stranger's shop
Fixed not being able to trade your reserve prank to The Stranger
Your prank in reserve will now be swapped to after trading your primary prank to The Stranger
Shoes now properly update after being traded to The Stranger
The camera will now recenter upon battle end with the classic control style enabled"
